{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9034a90dd0","title":"毛泽东对军队文化大革命的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2332f360e3","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"9034a90dd0"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"96ac69fed6","type":"title","text":"对军队文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9034a90dd0"},{"id":"8250685251","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9034a90dd0"},{"id":"7b888c720e","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 我认为十三个军区不要同时搞，要有前有后。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9034a90dd0"},{"id":"a659b5177b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 地方文化大革命正在猛烈开展，夺权斗争还在激烈进行，我们军队要支持地方革命左派进行夺权斗争，因此军队和地方文化大革命要叉开。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9034a90dd0"},{"id":"8fc37ea697","type":"paragraph","text":"三、 现在国际上帝、修、反正在利用我们文化大革命继续大搞反华活动。如苏联在镇压学生，新疆边境飞机活动多了，地面部队也在调动。凡是前线的大军区部队要有警惕，要有所准备。如济南、南京、福州、广州、昆明军区。所以文化大革命的时间要稍推一下。将来一定要搞的，顾大局。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9034a90dd0"}],"page":{"id":"7a21acc225","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9034a90dd0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}